<L>Quiltes of gold &thorn;ar vpon,<NOTE PLACE="foot">3857&mdash;3996:<Q><LG TYPE="stanza">
<L><I>Now is sere Sabeer ffor&thorn; igan:</I></L>
<L><I>Now god off heuene helpe Iosyan!</I></L>
<L><I>Now go&thorn; Saber ouer dale &amp; dounne,</I></L>
<L><I>Faste goynge to Mounbraunt tounne,</I></L>
<L N="5"><I>And as he wente for&thorn; in &thorn;at way,</I></L>
<L><I>He ouyr-took Iosyan, &thorn;at fayre may,</I></L>
<L><I>And Ascopard, &thorn;at wykkyd traytour,</I></L>
<L><I>And &thorn;rytty Sarezynys wi&thorn; good armour.</I></L>
<L><I>Saber gan to Iosyan wende</I></L>
<L N="10"><I>And here grette as kny&yogh;t so hende.</I></L>
<L><I>When Iosyan saw&yogh; &thorn;at hendy kny&yogh;t,</I></L>
<L><I>In here herte sche wax full ly&yogh;t;</I></L>
<L><I>Sche sayde: 'Sabeer, doo me sum red,</I></L>
<L><I>But &thorn;ou me helpe, I am but ded!'</I></L>
<L N="15"><I>Saber answerede: 'Fayre madame,</I></L>
<L><I>&THORN;ee to helpen hedyr we came!'</I></L>
<L><I>Sere Saber spak to hem anon:</I></L>
<L><I>'Traytours, &yogh;e schole deyen echon!'</I></L>
<L><I>&THORN;oo drow&yogh; hys burdoun eche palmere,</I></L>
<L N="20"><I>Sere Saber smoot sere Ascopard &thorn;ere</I></L>
<L><I>With hys burdoun in &thorn;e brest,</I></L>
<L><I>&THORN;at no lengere hys lyff ne lest;</I></L>
<L><I>&THORN;ey slowen &thorn;e sarezynys euerylkan,</I></L>
<L><I>And wi&thorn; hem token fayre Iosyan.</I></L>
<L N="25"><I>Sabeer hys felawys hoom ha&thorn; sent</I></L>
<L><I>And Iosyan ha&thorn; maad an oynement;</I></L>
<L><I>Here skyn, &thorn;at was bo&thorn;e bry&yogh;t &amp; schene,</I></L>
<L><I>&THORN;ere wi&thorn; sche made &yogh;elew and grene.</I></L>
<L><I>So &thorn;ey dy&yogh;ten &thorn;at fayre may,</I></L>
<L N="30"><I>&THORN;at men ne scholden ny&yogh;t ne day</I></L>
<L><I>Here knowen nower in no manere,</I></L>
<L><I>What sche was ne what sche were.</I></L>
<L><I>To geder VII</I><SUP>e</SUP> <I>&yogh;eer &thorn;ey haue sou&yogh;t,</I></L>
<L><I>But off B. ne Terry ffounde &thorn;ey nou&yogh;t.</I></L>
</LG><LG TYPE="stanza">
<L N="35"><I>&THORN;o it fyl vpon a day,</I></L>
<L><I>As &thorn;ey wenten in here iournay,</I></L>
