<L>&THORN;at &thorn;ai ner ded vpon &thorn;e grene,<MILESTONE UNIT="Turnbull line" N="3921"><NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>ner ded] ne died</I> SN. <I>Many of them dyd dye then</I> C.</NOTE></L>
<L>Eueri moder sone, i wene;<NOTE PLACE="foot"><I>By fyue, bi (or</I> S) <I>sixe, bi</I> (om. S) <I>twelf and (bi</I> N) <I>teen</I> SNC.</NOTE></L>
<L>And &thorn;us Saber in &thorn;is wise<NOTE PLACE="foot">4103&mdash;4108 om. SNC.</NOTE></L>
<L N="4104">Wan Arondel wi&thorn; is queintise.</L>
<L>Now mowe &yogh;e here for&thorn;ormore<MILESTONE UNIT="Turnbull line" N="3925"></L>
