<L N="4148">To Teruagaunt Yuor gan crie,</L>
<L>&THORN;at he scholde helpe him in &thorn;at fi&yogh;t,</L>
<L>Also he was king of meche mi&yogh;t.<MILESTONE UNIT="Turnbull line" N="3970">
<PB REF="00000283.tif" N="197"></L>
<L N="4151">Wi&thorn; &thorn;at hii ride to gedres bo&thorn;e,</L>
<L>Ase men, &thorn;at were in hertte wro&thorn;e,</L>
<L>So harde &thorn;ai gonne to gedres mete</L>
<L>And wi&thorn; here launces gonne grete,</L>
<L>&THORN;at &thorn;our&yogh; &thorn;e scheldes &thorn;e speres &yogh;ode;</L>
<L>At &thorn;e breinies &thorn;e dent wi&thorn;-stode.<MILESTONE UNIT="Turnbull line" N="3976"></L>
