<L>&THORN;at here ger&thorn;es borste ato,</L>
<L>&amp; felle to grounde bo&thorn;e &thorn;o,</L>
<L>A fote nedes &thorn;ai moste go.<MILESTONE UNIT="Turnbull line" N="3980"></L>
