<L>And wi&thorn; fauchouns to gedere flinge;</L>
<L>Ai&thorn;er on o&thorn;er strokes set,</L>
<L N="4164">Of helm and scheld and bacinet</L>
<L>&THORN;e fure brast out so brond ibrent,<MILESTONE UNIT="Turnbull line" N="3985"></L>
<L>So fel and eger was ei&thorn;er dent.</L>
